ar; Industrial Fibres and Related Products; and Chemicals. The company offers refined sugar, sugar cubes, fine sugar, and refined sugar sachets to pharmaceutical, food, home, hotels, airlines, railways, hospitals, restaurants, clubs, fast food chains, caterers, beverages, dairy products, and confectionery industries; and bulk alcohol products, such as rectified spirit, extra neutral alcohol, and anhydrous alcohol. It also provides rayon, synthetic yarn, tyre cord, and treated rayon fabric, as well as wicking and non-wicking nylon. In addition, it offers anhydrous sodium sulphate and carbon-di-sulphide, and organic and fine chemicals to agrochemicals, fragrance, paints, beverages, dairy products, confectionery, and other industries. Additionally, it offers armoured vehicles; containers; and hand sanitizers. DCM Shriram Industries Limited was founded in 1889 and is based in New Delhi, India."}}